725347f-b.title: Queens: 43rd Street - 55th Road
725347f-b.text:
(1)
43rd Street, west side, north from 55th Road, showing at the
S.W. corner of Fifty-fifth Ave. and 43rd Street, St. Mary's Episcopal
Church, which was organined in 1888.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, seen from Laurel Htll Boulevard, looking east and
showing a rear view.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
